snippet.title: SpiritSurge - Basement Bonanza Trailer
snippet.description:
https://crustsato.itch.io/spiritsurge
Our first trailer is here! This trailer primarily shows of the first half of the demo, in which our protagonists enter the basement of Travor Boarding School to look for the missing brother of a fellow student.
Like, subscribe and so on to help us out.
Our twitter: https://twitter.com/SpiritsurgeRPG
